reviewText: LOVED IT ALL.  WE LAUGHED SO MUCH THIS WAS WORTH BUYING REALLY A FUN SERIES

I'm from Texas and this is the funniest series I've ever watched!!  Everything about it was perfect!
Leading Actress and Actor were so enjoyable I wish they would make more comedy's together.
I just started watching Korean shows and have really enjoyed them!
This kdrama goes to our island. One of our favorites. Great cast. Great ending. Loved it from beginning till the end. Laugh out loud. Sweet. Romantic. Touching.
